00:01:26,163 --> 00:01:28,205
the idea that stuck with people is this.

22
00:01:28,205 --> 00:01:30,567
If you hope to be any good at anything,

23
00:01:30,567 --> 00:01:33,950
then you have to be doing one thing over and over again

24
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:35,111
for a very long time.

25
00:01:35,111 --> 00:01:38,074
