00:02:29,899 --> 00:02:34,740
It's the idea that you couldn't possibly be a polycreative,

43
00:02:34,740 --> 00:02:37,301
a polymath of creativity,

44
00:02:37,301 --> 00:02:41,022
someone who could create great things in more than one art form.

45
00:02:42,186 --> 00:02:45,850
It's also the idea that a franchise is not art.

46
00:02:45,850 --> 00:02:49,575
But I've created, consulted, and mentored, and judged

47
00:02:49,575 --> 00:02:51,818
hundreds and hundreds of transmedia projects

48
00:02:51,818 --> 00:02:52,599
around the world.

49
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:56,524
And I'm here to tell you that a franchise is something

50
00:02:56,524 --> 00:02:59,107
you can learn to craft, and I'll show you how.

51
00:03:01,137 --> 00:03:04,722
