53
00:03:07,646 --> 00:03:10,690
that you need to create webisodes on YouTube,

54
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:14,274
bring out novelizations and graphic novels, a feature film,

55
00:03:14,274 --> 00:03:16,817
some merchandise, and a soundtrack,

56
00:03:16,817 --> 00:03:18,520
and maybe do an alternate reality game.

57
00:03:19,562 --> 00:03:22,225
