00:09:41,798 --> 00:09:47,582
If we agree we all have this best practice of switching between our point of view and

171
00:09:47,582 --> 00:09:52,706
our players, of designing for leading promises and keeping them, then we have an approach

172
00:09:52,706 --> 00:09:55,988
that we can use across art forms in our franchise.

